Constructor Detail

IssuanceSpec

public IssuanceSpec(java.net.URI theCredStructLocation)
Create an issuance specification. An issuance specification loads the corresponding credential structure. The number of attributes which may be added is limited by the size of the IssuerPublicKey. This process is illustrated in the certificate issuance test cases.

Parameters:
theCredStructLocation - Location of the credential structure.
See Also:
IssuerPublicKey, CredentialStructure
